{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2641574, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？小朋友没有父亲怎么健康成长", "timestamp": 1633158167, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641575, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从小就让你的孩子没有选择地成为单亲家庭的孩子，也是有点惨", "timestamp": 1633158207, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641580, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641574, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 没有父亲就一定不能健康成长了？", "timestamp": 1633158246, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641584, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为啥要未婚生育…怎么这么想不开啊", "timestamp": 1633158291, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641586, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你既然愿意跟那个人生孩子，为什么不愿意跟那个人结婚呢", "timestamp": 1633158313, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641591, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641580, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你当然可以自信地说自己能教育好孩子，但是没有父亲确实是天生缺陷，小孩非常容易遭受社会环境的各方面压力", "timestamp": 1633158337, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641596, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641584, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 结婚有风险不是吗？当然肯定也有好处，风险厌恶的人不做出这个选择并不奇怪吧", "timestamp": 1633158416, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641599, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一个人养家吗？那你怎么边工作边照顾孩子？", "timestamp": 1633158451, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641596, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 显然未婚生孩子是一个比结婚更有风险的事情啊…我不明白，你既然风险厌恶，就更不应该做这种风险更大的事", "timestamp": 1633158515, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641604, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "速度，让社会不稳定更加一分，好时代来临力", "timestamp": 1633158520, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641606, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641591, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 没有父亲为什么是天生缺陷？有的孩子有父亲，但父亲并不称职，也会对孩子造成不好的影响吧", "timestamp": 1633158531, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641610, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641606, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这当然了，但是父亲在孩子成长中的地位是必然不可或缺的，有空可以阅读《发展心理学》等书籍", "timestamp": 1633158646, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641612, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641603, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我觉得你比较的两者不太对，应该是结婚生孩子和未婚生孩子比较。生育经历的风险都是一样的，关键在于少了一方家庭给予的支持，如果条件比较好，这部分问题不大", "timestamp": 1633158671, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641621, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "关于为什么未婚生育/怎么解决问题/父亲多么重要不想讨论了，帖子的重点是法律问题", "timestamp": 1633158856, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641622, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641621, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那你去精子银行做试管婴儿呗", "timestamp": 1633158886, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641656, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "居然还有这样的女人。要是全世界都是这样的女人，男人也太爽了", "timestamp": 1633159342, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641673, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "xjj可以上网搜一下“叶海洋”，她就是未婚生育了两个混血宝宝，长得特别好看。当然前提是自身能力强大啦，（参考叶海洋的个人能力），xjj冲！", "timestamp": 1633159512, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641684, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641656, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 恰恰相反吧哈哈哈哈，没有免费保姆负责做饭搞卫生照顾老人了（no offense to优秀男人，付出应该是双向的，但仍然有很多人认为是女生理所应当的", "timestamp": 1633159674, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641689, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641673, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 好！我去了解一下", "timestamp": 1633159777, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641691, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你是单纯的就喜欢小孩子吗…抱歉我是实在没法理解", "timestamp": 1633159819, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641700, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641691, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 啊，虽然我是打算结婚生子的，但是没觉得dz的想法有啥难理解的啊…", "timestamp": 1633160033, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641705, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641691, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 小朋友如果好好培养很可爱，值得一切的投入。没有非常喜欢（爸妈很喜欢），觉得有个小朋友也挺好", "timestamp": 1633160092, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2641732, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641705, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那你是很讨厌男人吗", "timestamp": 1633160422, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2642406, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": 2641691, "tag": null, "text": "洞主太悲观了吧，怎么就一口咬定没法找到和他能生孩子的人呢", "timestamp": 1633167363, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2647782, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 504196, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "理解洞主，暂时想法不婚不育，但如果单纯喜欢孩子的话也可以，🇫🇷那边好像这方面比较成熟，但国内未婚生育感觉风险确实不低～或许可以咨询下律师？", "timestamp": 1633238577, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 504196, "reply": 25, "tag": null, "text": "逐渐开始考虑未婚生育，觉得自己一个人可以承担风险。有没有懂法律的洞友科普下孩子与生物学父亲之间的权利和责任？比较担心小朋友长大以后和生物学父亲扯上关系", "timestamp": 1633158105, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1633238577, "url": "", "vote": {}}}